1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 exd5 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. Bd3 Bd6 6. O-O Nge7 {This game
was the second one of the World Cup. Bacrot won the first one with Black and
needs a draw with White.} 7. Nc3 Bg4 8. Nb5 f6 9. c3 Qd7 10. b4 O-O 11. Nxd6
