the mate!}) 19. b4 $18) 18... Kb8 19. Be4 g4 (19... b6 {Threatening ...Nxe5 is
not so clear.}) 20. hxg4 $2 (20. h4 $1 $16 Nxe5 21. Nxb7 $18) 20... hxg4 $13
21. Qxg4 {and now after} Rhg8 $1 (21... Nxe5 $2 22. Bxe5 Bxd6 23. Bxh8 Rxh8 24.
