[%csl Ra3]} 18. Bg4 Rc7 19. f5 {[%csl Ra3,Yd4,Yg4] The queen is misplaced on
a3 now and White's attack becomes very strong.} exf5 20. Bxf5 Bc8 21. Ng4 (21.
e6 $1 {was a powerful tactical blow, opening files and diagonals for White's
attack. For example:} Bxe6 (21... Nxe6 22. Be5) 22. Qf4 Rc6 23. Ng4 f6 24. Rde1
